Threat Plot (tplot) TODO list
==============

Short-term:
-----------
* Implement Hilbert curve plotting functionality
* Add IP geolocation database integration for timezone mapping
* Implement timezone-aware visualization
* Add support for multiple honeypot log formats
* Add configurable time domain selection

Long-term:
----------
* Add interactive visualization interface
* Support for real-time data streaming
* Add multiple visualization curve options beyond Hilbert curves
* Pattern detection and anomaly highlighting
* Export functionality for visualizations
